Title: Hello, Stranger!
Description: My name is Sailor, and I am native Iowan cat. I live in West Des Moines, and I am a plump man in full bloom!

Title: I like IT devices!
Description: In my house there are a lot of wierd things.They make a lot of weird noises and keep me warm, I like 'em!

Title: I like to hunt paper rolls!
Description: If you want to keep me entertained - give me a paper roll. I will show the real cats' nature!

Title: I like the spooky Halloween!
Description: All my quality time I spend outside the house. I like walking, hunting, and sleep on the open air.

Title: I like sleeping in the Garden.
Description: Garden is outside, and I like being outside!

Title: I am a great listener.
Description: Me-ow listen without distractions, don't pre-judge the messages, keep eyes on the speaker, and communicate interest.

Title: I am super cute!
Description: You see I am cute, and I know how to use feline wiles to lure you into forking over some extra yum yums..

Title: I am a great mice hunter!
Description: No worries, no mice get in the house from the basement!

Title: Be Happy and Smile!
Description: This is my piece of advice to YOU! Thank you for visiting my web site!
